text_question_merge: Hlanganisa amanqaku akhoyo kunye namanqaku angenisiweyo okanye ubeke endaweni yawo?
text_importexport_content: Apha ungangenisa kwaye uthumele ngaphandle amanqaku akho.
text_help_content2: Ukwenza inowuthi entsha, okanye incwadi eneenkcukacha entsha, cinezela i "plus" icon: khetha phakathi kwenowuthi kunye nefolda, faka isihloko kwaye ekugqibeleni umxholo, emva koko ucinezele ukugcina ukugcina utshintsho, okanye ucofe ukucima ukucima inqaku, okanye ubuyisele ukutsiba utshintsho kodwa gcina inqaku.
text_help_content3: Cofa iqhosha "vula" kufutshane nenqaku ukuvula umxholo onxulumene noko.
text_help_content4: Cinezela "ukongeza" iqhosha ngaphakathi kwifolda ukongeza into entsha kuyo.
text_help_content5: Kuzo zombini amanqaku kunye neefolda, cofa iqhosha u "hlela" ukuzitshintsha, cofa iqhosha u "buyisela umva" ukutshintshiselana ngesikhundla kunye nento yangaphambili, cofa iqhosha u "qhubela phambili" ukutshintshiselana ngendawo kunye nento elandelayo, cofa u "yiya phezulu" iqhosha lokususa umba kwifolda apho ikhoyo ngoku, okanye cinezela "yiya ezantsi" iqhosha ukuhambisa umlinganiso ngaphakathi kwifolda elandelayo.
text_help_content6: Kwimenyu yezicwangciso, efikelelekayo emva kokucofa i "iisetingi" icon, unokufihla okanye ubonise ukuhlela, intshukumo kunye namaqhosha okongeza. Ungaqwalasela kwakhona imigca yendawo yokubhaliweyo kunye neekholamu zebhokisi yencoko "yokuhlela". Kuyenzeka ukuba utshintshe ulwimi lomsebenzisi.
text_help_content7: Ukungenisa ngaphakathi okanye ukuhambisa ngaphandle amanqaku, cofa kwi icon yokungenisa / ukuthumela ngaphandle. Amanqaku aya kungeniswa ngaphakathi okanye athunyelwe kwelinye ilizwe kwifayile yeJSON ethe ngqo kule app. Xa ungenisa amanqaku kwifayile, amanqaku akhoyo aya kucinywa kwaye abhalwe ngaphezulu.
text_help_content8: Amanqaku sisicelo seWebhu esiqhubela phambili, oko kuthetha ukuba siyasebenza ngaphakathi kwisikhangeli. Xa uyifaka, ngelixa izinto zebrawuza zingaboniswanga, iqhubeka ngaphakathi kwisikhangeli. Amanqaku agcinwa kwindawo yogcino lwasekhaya kwindawo yogcino lwamanqaku.marcoparrone.com. Indawo yogcino isebenza kakuhle kunye nezikhangeli zeChannel, Edge kunye neFirefox. Ezinye iibrawuza zinokucima ugcino lwasekhaya emva kwexesha elithile. I-Android ngokungagqibekanga isebenzisa iChannel, iiWindows ngokungagqibekanga zisebenzisa iEdge. Amanqaku okwangoku akaxhaswanga kwiimveliso ze-Apple. Ngenjongo yokunceda ukukhusela ukulahleka kwamanqaku, kucetyiswa ukuba wenze isipele usebenzisa ukusebenza "kokuthumela ngaphandle", ngalo lonke ixesha usenza uhlengahlengiso ongafuni kulahleka.
text_about_content3: I-SOFTWARE IBONELELWA "NJENGOKO INJALO", NGAPHANDLE KWESIQINISEKISO SALO LONKE IINTLOBO, UKUCHAZA OKANYE OKUFAKANISIWEYO, KUBANDAKANYWA KODWA AKUKHO MALI KWIZIQINISEKISO ZOKUTHENGISA, UKULUNGELELA INJONGO ETHILE NOKUNGABONI. text_about_content4: LENKONZO INGABA NEZINGUQUKO EZIXHASWA YI-GOOGLE. UGOOGLE ULAWULA ZONKE IZIQINISEKISO ZOKUNXULUMANA NOKUTSHINTSHA, UKUCHAZA OKANYE OKUFUNYANISIWEYO, KUFUNYANWA NASIPHI ISIQINISEKISO SOKUCHANEKA, UKUTHEMBEKA, KUNYE NAZO ZONKE IZIQINISEKISO ZOKWENZA UMSEBENZI, UKULUNGELELA INJONGO ETHILE NOKUNGABONI.
text_about_content5: Le app yewebhu iguqulelwe ukulungiselela wena usebenzisa isoftware yokuguqulela exhaswa nguToliko lukaGoogle. Iinzame ezisengqiqweni zenziwe ukubonelela ngoguqulelo oluchanekileyo, nangona kunjalo, akukho nguqulelo ezenzekelayo engagqibelelanga kwaye ayenzelwanga ukubuyisela abaguquleli abangabantu. Iinguqulelo zinikezelwa njengenkonzo kubasebenzisi bewebhusayithi ye marcoparrone.com, kwaye zinikezelwa "njengoko kunjalo." Akukho waranti yalo naluphi na uhlobo, nokuba ichaziwe okanye icacisiwe, yenziwa ngokuchaneka, ukuthembeka, okanye ukuchaneka kwazo naziphi na iinguqulelo ezenziwe ngesiNgesi kulo naluphi na ulwimi. Eminye imixholo (enjengemifanekiso, iividiyo, iFlash, njl. Njl.) Ayinakho ukuguqulelwa ngokuchanekileyo ngenxa yemida yesoftware yokuguqulela.
text_about_content6: Isicatshulwa esisemthethweni yinguqulelo yesiNgesi yewebhusayithi. Nakuphi na ukungangqinelani okanye iyantlukwano edalwe kuguqulelo ayibopheleli kwaye ayinampembelelo yomthetho yokuthotyelwa okanye yokunyanzeliswa. Ukuba kukho nayiphi na imibuzo enxulumene nokuchaneka kolwazi oluqulathwe kwiwebhusayithi eguqulweyo, bhekisa kwinguqulelo yesiNgesi yewebhusayithi leyo eluhlobo olusemthethweni.
